a simple toy socket programming application

* server
  implemented in common lisp (sbcl)

  - dependency
    closs/port
    log5

  - usage (from src/server directory as current-directory)
    toy-user@toy-computer$ sbcl --load program.lisp

    or

    toy-user@toy-computer$ emacs
    [inside emacs]
    M-x slime
    [on slime prompt]
    (load "program")


* client
  implemented in java

  - usage
    toy-user@toy-computer$ cd src/client
    toy-user@toy-computer$ ant
